                <li>Add new book to the list using <b>New Book</b> from the header</li>
                <li>Change the content using <b>edit</b> icon</li>
                <li>Sort by rating or recency</li>
                <li>Delete the book using <b>delete</b> iconn where a <b>modal</b> window will appear</li>
                <li>Search for a book from your list using search input</li>
